Package ninja.validation

Annotation Type IsEnum

  • @Retention(RUNTIME)
@Target(PARAMETER)
public @interface IsEnum
    Validates that the field is a valid enum constant. Only needed if you want to customise the validation messages.
    Author:
    James Moger
